13556.「ここが あやしいってワケかい？:
So you're saying you think this place is
shady?

13557.「なるほど。アンタ カンが さえてるね。\n 確かに お宝のにおいが プンプンす:
I see. You have a good instinct, don't you?
Indeed, I can smell treasure.

13558.「よし！ それじゃ 今度は\n あたいのカンを 見せつけてやろうかね。:
Okay! Well then, let me show you my instincts
this time.

13559.「ここら辺に ありそうな気が……。: I think it might be around here somewhere.

13560.「よっしゃ！ 見つけたよ！\n お宝 ムーンダイヤモンド！: Yes! I found it! Treasure Moon Diamond!

13562.「その お宝は オレたちのもんだー！！\n だまって よこしやがれー！！\n キ:
That treasure is ours! Give it to us! Kicky-
kicky!

13564.「なんだい こいつら！！\n お宝は 渡さないよっ！！:
What the hell are they doing? You can't have
the treasure!

13565.「ダルルのあねごを 助けるんだ！\n 行くぞ <cs_pchero>！:
We've got to save Darul's anego! Let's go
<cs_pchero>!

13566.「やあ <cs_pchero>。\n 心配しなくても ムーンダイヤモンドは\n:
Hey <cs_pchero>. Don't worry, Moon Diamond
is still in this room.

13567.「前回 魔物に襲われたとき\n とっさに ムーンダイヤモンドを\n かくしておい:
The last time I was attacked by a monster, I
hid the Moon Diamond.

13570.「そんな所に かくしてやがったのかー！！\n だまって そいつを よこしやがれー:
You hid it there! Stop it and give me the damn
thing! Kicky-kicky!

13572.「今度こそ ダルルのあねごを 助けるんだ！\n 行くぞ <cs_pchero>！:
This time we're going to save Darul's anegos!
Let's go <cs_pchero>!

13573.「……キキーッ！！\n オレたちに たてつくとは バカなヤツめっ！\n それっ:
Kickin'! You're the one who's doing this
against us, you idiot! Report that to the
head!

13574.「<cs_pchero>！ アンタ 強いんだねえ！\n やっぱ あたいの目に\n:
<cs_pchero>! You're so strong! I knew there
was nothing wrong with my eyes!

13576.「さっきの魔物ですが……。\n あいつら つむじ風の旅団かもしれませんぜ。:
That monster you saw earlier... they might be
the Whirlwind Brigade.

13577.「つむじ風の旅団……。\n あの 強盗を なりわいにした\n 魔物たちの盗賊集団:
The Whirlwind Brigade... you know, that band
of thieves made robbery their profession, a
group of monsters?

13578.「単なる うわさ話だと思ってたけど\n この目で 見ちまったんじゃあ\n ほうっ:
I thought it was just a rumor, but now that
I've seen it with my own eyes, I can't just
leave it at that.

13579.「よし わかった。\n ガタラに戻ったら やつらの情報を\n 集めてみるとしよう:
Okay, I get it. I'll try to get some
information on them when I get back to Gatara.

13580.「ああ <cs_pchero> すまなかったね。\n なにはともあれ アンタのお:
Oh <cs_pchero> I'm sorry. At any rate,
thanks to you, I now have the Moon Diamond.

13581.「今回の報酬は ガタラの酒場で\n 山分けするとしよう。\n あたいらは 先に戻:
We'll split the reward this time at Gatara's
tavern. We'll go back first and wait for you.
